                    <div class="doc-item">
                        <h2>Privacy First</h2>
                        
                        <h3>Data Transmission</h3>
                        <p>ContainEye does not send any of your commands to my servers. All SSH and test commands are sent directly from your device to your server.</p>

                        <h3>How AI handles data</h3>
                        <p>AI is used purely for generating test suggestions. It never sees your passwords or sensitive credentials. Commands are only executed after your explicit confirmation.</p>

                        <h3>Analytics</h3>
                        <p>I collect minimal, anonymized usage statistics to help improve the app. This data is GDPR-compliant and contains no personal information.</p>
